profiles/machine/snapmaker_u1_0_4_nozzle.json
=================================================

Derived from upstream OrcaSlicer v2.4.0's bundled Snapmaker vendor profiles:

  resources/profiles/Snapmaker/machine/Snapmaker U1 (0.4 nozzle).json
  resources/profiles/Snapmaker/machine/fdm_U1.json
  resources/profiles/Snapmaker/machine/fdm_toolchanger.json
  resources/profiles/Snapmaker/machine/fdm_klipper.json

Those source files were originally contributed by Snapmaker to OrcaSlicer
upstream. OrcaSlicer is licensed under AGPL-3.0.

The bundled file in this directory is a *flattened* version — the full
4-level inheritance chain was merged into one standalone JSON so headless
CLI slicing works without needing Orca to find each parent in its install
resources. The flattening was done mechanically; no field values were
modified.

If you'd rather use upstream Orca's original (non-flattened) vendor
profiles, install OrcaSlicer 2.4.0+ and load:

  <orca-install>/resources/profiles/Snapmaker/machine/Snapmaker U1 (0.4 nozzle).json

instead of this bundled copy.
